<h3 local-id=3D"777f1acf3b82" id=3D"Research-Tu=C3=A2nth=E1=BB=A7AgenticAI-=
8.2Stackph=C3=A1thi=E1=BB=87nn=E1=BB=99idung(ContentDetectionStack)">8.2 St=
ack ph=C3=A1t hi=E1=BB=87n n=E1=BB=99i dung (Content Detection Stack)</h3>
<p local-id=3D"560f09939ca7">C=C3=A1c l=E1=BB=9Bp ch=E1=BA=A1y theo th=E1=
=BB=A9 t=E1=BB=B1, d=E1=BB=ABng khi c=C3=B3 quy=E1=BA=BFt =C4=91=E1=BB=8Bnh=
 r=C3=B5 r=C3=A0ng:</p>
<p local-id=3D"757d096788c0"><strong>L=E1=BB=9Bp 1 - Rule-based filter</str=
ong></p>
<p local-id=3D"af64eb05b16e">Regex, keyword blocklist, pattern matching. La=
tency d=C6=B0=E1=BB=9Bi 5ms, kh=C3=B4ng c=E1=BA=A7n GPU. Hi=E1=BB=87u qu=E1=
=BA=A3 v=E1=BB=9Bi clear violation - c=C3=B3 th=E1=BB=83 b=E1=BA=AFt 60=E2=
=80=9370% c=C3=A1c tr=C6=B0=E1=BB=9Dng h=E1=BB=A3p vi ph=E1=BA=A1m r=C3=B5 =
r=C3=A0ng v=E1=BB=9Bi chi ph=C3=AD g=E1=BA=A7n nh=C6=B0 b=E1=BA=B1ng kh=C3=
=B4ng.</p>
<p local-id=3D"7f33a5c511fa">Ph=C3=B9 h=E1=BB=A3p nh=E1=BA=A5t cho: PII pat=
terns (email, phone, ID numbers, credit card), credential formats (API key,=
 token), domain-specific blocked terms.</p>
<p local-id=3D"f1f780c8f1f4"></p>
<p local-id=3D"0473178cd477"><strong>L=E1=BB=9Bp 2 - PII Detection &amp; Re=
daction</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"6e692b1cc4eb">NER model chuy=C3=AAn bi=E1=BB=87t =C4=91=E1=
=BB=83 ph=C3=A1t hi=E1=BB=87n v=C3=A0 mask th=C3=B4ng tin c=C3=A1 nh=C3=A2n=
. Ch=E1=BA=A1y tr=C3=AAn c=E1=BA=A3 input c=E1=BB=A7a ng=C6=B0=E1=BB=9Di d=
=C3=B9ng v=C3=A0 output c=E1=BB=A7a tool (=C4=91=E1=BA=B7c bi=E1=BB=87t qua=
n tr=E1=BB=8Dng =E1=BB=9F =C4=91i=E1=BB=83m =E2=91=A2 - tool output scan).<=
/p>
<p local-id=3D"04e224412f64">L=E1=BB=B1a ch=E1=BB=8Dn gi=E1=BA=A3i ph=C3=A1=
p: SpaCy v=E1=BB=9Bi custom NER, AWS Comprehend, ho=E1=BA=B7c Azure AI Lang=
uage PII Detection.</p>
<p local-id=3D"5d5baae747ff"></p>
<p local-id=3D"8bfc87c9a131"><strong>L=E1=BB=9Bp 3 - Embedding Similarity</=
strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"d6e348fbb0a4">So s=C3=A1nh input v=E1=BB=9Bi vector database=
 ch=E1=BB=A9a c=C3=A1c known-bad prompt (jailbreak patterns, injection sign=
atures). Hi=E1=BB=87u qu=E1=BA=A3 v=E1=BB=9Bi paraphrase attack v=C3=A0 ind=
irect injection m=C3=A0 keyword search b=E1=BB=8F qua.</p>
<p local-id=3D"a555917ee089">Vector database c=E1=BA=A7n =C4=91=C6=B0=E1=BB=
=A3c c=E1=BA=ADp nh=E1=BA=ADt li=C3=AAn t=E1=BB=A5c sau m=E1=BB=97i inciden=
t v=E1=BB=9Bi pattern m=E1=BB=9Bi =C4=91=C6=B0=E1=BB=A3c ph=C3=A1t hi=E1=BB=
=87n.</p>
<p local-id=3D"fe2a2b379e43"></p>
<p local-id=3D"08f448fad8f7"><strong>L=E1=BB=9Bp 4 - Safety Classifier</str=
ong></p>
<p local-id=3D"1666d5390bae">Model ph=C3=A2n lo=E1=BA=A1i multi-label v=E1=
=BB=9Bi confidence score cho t=E1=BB=ABng category trong taxonomy. =C4=90=
=C3=A2y l=C3=A0 layer ch=C3=ADnh x=E1=BB=AD l=C3=BD ph=E1=BA=A7n l=E1=BB=9B=
n content moderation.</p>
<p local-id=3D"55c724c7ab9e">L=E1=BB=B1a ch=E1=BB=8Dn off-the-shelf =C4=91=
=C3=A3 =C4=91=C6=B0=E1=BB=A3c validate:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"95cb072a-e453-4394-93bb-7d31ac1d862b">
<li local-id=3D"372a8a74-29b0-4469-9d5d-24fbcff4d950">
<p local-id=3D"d8d1ff20e8a7"><strong>Open source:</strong> Llama Guard (Met=
a), Aegis-Guard</p></li>
